data.description: Beautifully updated 4bed/2bath in Holly Hills with 2 car garage, bonus room, large laundry room, and Fully fenced backyard! This fantastic family home was fully updated in 2017 featuring a Gleaming Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Stainless Appliances, Gorgeous Cabinetry and a Large Pantry; Beautiful Hardwood floors in the Entryway and living spaces, two fully renovated bathrooms, new windows throughout, a 2017 Roof, Large Deck overlooking the backyard and a bonus/flex room (currently used as an extra Den). This home has it all and won't last long! Seller offering a $2500 flooring allowance to replace carpet in bedrooms.
